Klasse DataAggregator

java.lang.Object
app.logic.DataAggregator
public class DataAggregator extends Object
Provides helper methods to compute aggregated drone data.

    • getAverageSpeedPerType

      public static Map<String,Double> getAverageSpeedPerType()
      Calculates the average speed for each drone type. Uses drone dynamics data grouped by drone type.
      Gibt zurück:
      map of drone type to average speed

    • getBatteryDistribution

      public static Map<String,Long> getBatteryDistribution()
      Groups drones into battery level ranges. Useful for displaying battery health distribution.
      Gibt zurück:
      map of battery range label to count

    • getBatteryDistributionFiltered

      public static Map<String,Long> getBatteryDistributionFiltered(Map<String, List<DroneDynamics>> dronesByType)
      Groups drones into battery level ranges, but only for a filtered set of drones.
      Parameter:
      dronesByType - map from drone labels to their dynamics lists
      Gibt zurück:
      map of battery range label to count

    • getTopDroneTypes

      public static Map<String,Integer> getTopDroneTypes()
      Finds the most common drone types in the dataset. Counts how many drones belong to each type and returns the top 5.
      Gibt zurück:
      map of top 5 drone types with their counts (sorted descending)
